<h3 id="convertir-de-decimal-a-binario">Convertir de Decimal a Binario</h3>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>2<sup>7</sup></th>
      <th>2<sup>6</sup></th>
      <th>2<sup>5</sup></th>
      <th>2<sup>4</sup></th>
      <th>2<sup>3</sup></th>
      <th>2<sup>2</sup></th>
      <th>2<sup>1</sup></th>
      <th>2<sup>0</sup></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>128</td>
      <td>64</td>
      <td>32</td>
      <td>16</td>
      <td>8</td>
      <td>4</td>
      <td>2</td>
      <td>1</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p><br />
<strong>Ejemplo</strong><br />
convertir 78<br />
comparamos el 78 con cada numero</p>

<pre>
78 &gt;= 128 = No 
78 &gt;= 64  = SI -&gt; 78 - 64 = 14  
14 &gt;= 32  = NO  
14 &gt;= 16  = NO  
14 &gt;= 8   = SI -&gt; 14 - 8  = 6
6  &gt;= 4   = SI -&gt; 6  - 4  = 2
2  &gt;= 2   = SI -&gt; 2  - 2  = 0
0  &gt;= 1   = NO
</pre>

<p>REMPLAZAMOS LOS SI POR 1 en la tabla</p>

